---
layout: "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro"
title: "About"
---

<!-- About Page - Fishnini Fantasy World -->
<section class="relative min-h-screen w-full text-white bg-black overflow-hidden font-serif">
  <!-- Fullscreen Background Image -->
  <img src="/images/about-hero.png" alt="Mystical Forest" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover z-0" />

  <!-- Overlay Gradient and Blur -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/70 via-purple-900/60 to-black/80 z-10 backdrop-blur-sm"></div>

  <!-- Twinkling Star Layer -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-20 pointer-events-none starfield"></div>

  <!-- Content Container -->
  <div class="relative z-30 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-28 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-yellow-100 drop-shadow mb-6 animate-fade-in">
      ✧ Welcome to <span class="text-pink-300">Fishnini</span> ✧
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-purple-100 leading-relaxed mb-10 animate-slide-up">
      A land reborn through starlight and memory. Here, foxes paint dreams and owls whisper names once lost. You are not escaping — you are remembering.
    </p>

    <!-- Glowing Scroll Card -->
    <div class="bg-white/10 border border-white/20 backdrop-blur-md rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-2xl max-w-3xl mx-auto animate-zoom-in">
      <p class="text-white/90 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        ✧ In the glades of Fishnini, every leaf tells your tale.<br />
        ✧ The stars hum lullabies for forgotten hearts.<br />
        ✧ You didn’t arrive by chance — the forest called you.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Button -->
    <div class="mt-14">
      <a href="#top" class="inline-block bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-400 via-purple-500 to-yellow-300 text-black font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-full shadow-xl hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
        ↑ Back to Top
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
@keyframes fade-in {
  from { opacity: 0; }
  to { opacity: 1; }
}
@keyframes slide-up {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}
@keyframes zoom-in {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.95); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
}
.animate-fade-in { animation: fade-in 1s ease-out forwards; }
.animate-slide-up { animation: slide-up 1.2s ease-out forwards; }
.animate-zoom-in { animation: zoom-in 1.4s ease-out forwards; }

.starfield {
  background-image: radial-gradient(white 0.8px, transparent 0.8px);
  background-size: 30px 30px;
  animation: twinkle 5s ease-in-out infinite;
  opacity: 0.06;
}
@keyframes twinkle {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 0.05; }
  50% { opacity: 0.12; }
}

h1, h2, h3 {
  font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif;
}
p {
  font-family: 'IM Fell English', serif;
}
</style>

